data.text:
VIRTUAL WINTER WORKSHOP is a 3-day event featuring an assortment of online classes led by experienced faculty. The only equipment required is your computer and a solid internet connection. Having bells at home may enhance the experience of some of the courses but is not required. You will have the opportunity to attend classes live, and be provided with access to watch all classes for 30 days following the event.

To learn more about the classes and instructors, see below.
